<subSubSection pageId="148" pageNumber="546" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="148.[174,1380,1513,2294]" pageId="148" pageNumber="546">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[176,540,2064,2097]" pageId="148" pageNumber="546">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. The Greater Congo Shrew is known from only a single specimen collected in 1955. Further research is needed on distribution, abundance, general ecology, and threats to this species.
</paragraph>
